        <h1 class="article-title">Cable Management Solutions — The Complete Guide</h1>
        <p class="article-lead">Everything you need to know to tame the rat's nest under your desk. Zip ties, cable trays, sleeves, raceways, standing-desk tricks, and a full step-by-step — no matter your budget.</p>
      </div>
